# SafeBasket frontend configuration.
#
# In local dev you can leave this empty: Vite proxies /api and /health to the
# backend on http://localhost:8000 (see vite.config.js).
#
# In production (Lovable / Netlify / Cloudflare Pages / etc.) set this to the
# public URL of the deployed Python API, e.g. https://api.safebasket.co.in
# On Lovable, add it under Cloud/Project → Secrets as VITE_API_BASE_URL.

# VITE_API_BASE_URL=https://api.safebasket.co.in
